title: Ohio State vs. Penn State live stream, tv schedule: Where to watch the Buckeyes Saturday night
text:
Where can you watch Ohio State vs. Penn State Saturday? Here's everything you need to know. 
Kickoff is set for 8 p.m. at Ohio Stadium in Columbus 
The Buckeyes' grip as the No. 1 team in the nation has been slipping for weeks. More and more teams are stealing away more and more top votes in the AP poll. Ohio State obviously hasn't faltered in its national championship defense, but after playing down to its opponents time and time again, people are beginning to sour on Urban Meyer's squad a bit. 
Can Penn State take advantage of Ohio State's penchant for starting slow? The Nittany Lions haven't exactly been world beaters themselves. 
Here's the important television and online viewing information for the game: Penn State at No. 1 Ohio State Kickoff: 8 p.m.
